oom_01.png", "id": "332281102302816", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39036629_332281108969482_4697895475146858678_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=2zTmo2QwALQQ7kNvgGdgmiy&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBrlPOtM2V_okMPFS7p5NuUsw8SO-Rr8YzBbUOqeqDM7g&oe=676808C1"}, {"file_name": "Lobby_02.png", "id": "694455891679972", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974862_694455895013305_5365825317235734912_n.png?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=KBRiTeZnimoQ7kNvgGxItB4&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDBElsiGcLSFh42JT2V9Gl8GI45n7822w5LqKM-KY-Q9Q&oe=6767EC55"}, {"file_name": "Interview_01.png", "id": "558098475502894", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982460_558098478836227_2195642163881727498_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=0RHj4HismfoQ7kNvgFditDA&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDs_Zn8_Dz5GPxwrYp5l4-luD2ahFmTfhtqkDGe45MlRg&oe=676808CE"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "JOb INterview Simulator (4).png", "id": "371985591479423", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39035469_371985598146089_1320847157226308449_n.png?_nc_cat=110&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=ZxHA_ADxzBcQ7kNvgG5L5zu&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBXqG4TU_d-qldDrj0sMCUR22BNzO6BTGvx7dQ1HfNCZQ&oe=67680850"}, "display_name": "Job Interview Simulator", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Proficient job interviewing craft is vital to attain the careers of our dreams. Unfortunately, it's difficult to practice this skill in a realistic way.\n\nThat's why we built the Job Interview Simulator. Simulate the entire interviewing process; from emailing HR before the interview, picking an outfit, arriving on time, catching the elevator, greeting the receptionist, and acing the interview. \n\nFeel the situational pressure of a Job Interview in an immersive virtual 